.TH LOA-LIST 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
list \- Show all items
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> list
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Displays the full collection in a table.
.TP
Columns include item type, progress, read state, and location.
.TP
Use \fBlist full\fR to include language, instrumentation, and other extended metadata columns.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> list
.TP
alexandria> list language german
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-list-sheet(1), loa-list-language(1), loa-list-instrument(1), loa-list-genre(1), loa-list-tag(1)
